00:02:21,255 --> 00:02:23,376
I have to dive into it a little bit.

52
00:02:24,824 --> 00:02:26,724
As we step through the Stone Mason level,

53
00:02:26,744 --> 00:02:28,145
I will keep coming back here a lot.

54
