Basically, what we are going to do is go over six major rules

57
00:02:34,266 --> 00:02:35,246
from God of War's levels.

58
00:02:35,266 --> 00:02:38,086
There will be a little bit of time for questions at the end.

59
00:02:38,106 --> 00:02:42,067
If we run out of time, I can meet you at room 305 or 308,

60
00:02:42,407 --> 00:02:43,747
and we can keep discussing.

61
00:02:44,368 --> 00:02:46,708
My hope is that by showing you these rules

