1256
00:53:53,412 --> 00:53:55,733
But as you can see, the pure nature of a circle

1257
00:53:55,793 --> 00:53:57,574
doesn't really give the environment team

1258
00:53:57,994 --> 00:53:59,955
much wiggle room to deliver on the fantasy

1259
00:53:59,975 --> 00:54:02,336
of a fabulous Norse lush landscape, right?

1260
00:54:02,916 --> 00:54:05,497
