1294
00:55:25,977 --> 00:55:27,398
and a lot of variety in each level

1295
00:55:27,458 --> 00:55:29,558
is going to drive themes and make things fun, right?

1296
00:55:30,779 --> 00:55:32,639
You can see how having a hub will be a good,

1297
00:55:32,739 --> 00:55:35,780
overarching wrapper to a game and to an exploration experience.

1298
00:55:36,480 --> 00:55:38,761
