00:55:41,882 --> 00:55:43,342
or additional creative challenges

1302
00:55:43,402 --> 00:55:44,563
that we're trying to solve together,

1303
00:55:44,963 --> 00:55:47,404
a design classic can sort of let you predict head a little bit.

1304
00:55:47,744 --> 00:55:49,784
You're confident that it's going to come together,

1305
00:55:50,144 --> 00:55:51,445
and you can focus a little bit more

1306
00:55:51,505 --> 00:55:52,625
on the day-over-day challenges.

1307
00:55:53,607 --> 00:55:56,309
