1317
00:56:14,362 --> 00:56:16,083
You do need a strong foundation, and you

1318
00:56:16,123 --> 00:56:17,604
do need a strong design canvas.

1319
00:56:17,944 --> 00:56:20,766
But a canvas is not inherently interesting on its own.

1320
00:56:21,227 --> 00:56:22,588
So I'll leave you with one final rule.

